{
  "id": "RAW_0a76fc2b",
  "title": "跨层压缩隐藏状态同时加速 TTFT 和压缩 KV cache!",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651001361&idx=3&sn=1a2b6621f118683fe09b0ea8701d3926",
  "date": "2025-11-13 04:09:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们都知道 LLM 中存在结构化稀疏性，但其底层机制一直缺乏统一的理论解释。为什么模型越深，稀疏性越明显？为什么会出现所谓的「检索头」和「检索层」？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们非常荣幸地宣布，我们试图回答这些问题的论文 UNCOMP 已被 EMNLP 2025 主会接收！我们不仅提出了一个高效的推理框架，更重要的是，我们提供了一个全新的理论视角来理解 LLM 内部的信息动态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517128\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.08148148148148149\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:562px;height:46px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOCVSsodEPwlTHsibjKg3fRwEMXGWuqwZ5g53Se8ZibK8uV2vQJDicqdLiaA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy2=\"88.39857651245552\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7271f4f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW9MJaGgnUWevWy2EePDqGWma9Z6COeZUx5KZrCULV06zuPVjrzrLM4NsdFWZHVdYY2U99ppKJkjIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">UNComp: Can Matrix Entropy Uncover Sparsity? -- A Compressor Design from an Uncertainty-Aware Perspective</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.03090\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.03090</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">GitHub：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/menik1126/UNComp\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/menik1126/UNComp</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"503517118\" data-ratio=\"0.6506550218340611\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"916\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44d892a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskO8r7XC4Fw5JCy6rt2DxPiccbg1BoYNMoIf9FhZj258pZ3kMAAzrLFBlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517119\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.1833550065019507\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"769\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1fcc11d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOyaUx6pjX9BRr2yhZ3S2CZF312OyicibWNdYKY29TgQVgJFjcrXYNbSwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🔬 核心洞察：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">一个关于熵的悖论与新解</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">传统的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">矩阵熵 (Matrix Entropy)&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">分析存在一个悖论：它显示信息熵随着层数加深是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">逐层增加</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的。这与我们观察到的「模型越深越稀疏」的现象相矛盾。如果信息在不断累积，又何来稀疏一说？🧐</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们的关键突破在于引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">截断矩阵熵 (Truncated Matrix Entropy)</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。通过分析 Token 矩阵协方差奇异值分布的「拐点」，我们只关注最重要的主成分。惊人的发现是：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">✨ 截断矩阵熵随着层数加深，呈现出明显的逐层递减趋势！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这不仅完美解释了深层网络的稀疏化现象，也为我们的压缩策略提供了坚实的理论基础。熵的减少意味着信息变得更加集中和稀疏，为压缩创造了空间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🌊 从理论到实践：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">信息流的指引</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这个理论工具让我们能「看透」模型的内部运作：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517120\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.45654565456545654\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"909\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=76868548&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOlPzEDg1KIgR2VOIZIYib7MV1sslibFZN2Xz5gkNkeRRHbX8ltv8iayrDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">识别关键结构：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中间层信息熵的异常波动点，精准地对应了负责信息聚合的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">检索层 (Retrieval Layers)和负责长程记忆的检索头 (Retrieval Heads)</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。我们不再是盲目压缩，而是有理论指导的结构化剪枝。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517121\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8488063660477454\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"754\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=542b86a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOuAWI6tsogWOQZbqRfgteYtxm0Lugic04ygNeXfnANoeiablEPlQ9R1Ng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">最优压缩的奥秘：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们进一步分析发现，最佳的压缩性能和最终的准确率的权衡并非来自于寻找最优的累计注意力分布，而是来自于对「信息流模式」的模仿。我们用皮尔逊相关系数证明：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">当压缩后 KV Cache 的逐层熵变趋势，与原始全尺寸 Cache 的趋势高度相似时，模型性能最好。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;这意味着，我们的压缩策略成功地保留了模型原有的信息压缩模式。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517122\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6178428761651131\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"751\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cc6ca718&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOHzGxty6fvSsAMuuSUSzjvGWwyDo6QbLq9FIzxuiaJlHkY0nqjJugw5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Group Query Attention 结构中呈现出明显的头共享的稀疏模式。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🚀 首创：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">从隐藏状态压缩到 KV Cache 优化</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于以上理论，我们设计了 UNCOMP 框架，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">并首次通过直接压缩 Prefill 阶段的隐藏状态，来间接优化 KV Cache</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，实现了计算与内存的联合优化。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">层级压缩 (Layer-wise):</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;在 Prefill 阶段压缩隐藏状态，加速计算。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">头级压缩 (Head-wise):&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Decoding 阶段压缩流式头的 KV Cache，保留检索头,节省内存。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517123\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0541125541125542\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"924\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=768c890a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOoyw66SrOdhRQ3rE0M0cicdG3ICwxlStibcwqquSSzQS74ThQfjg6DzJg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">📊 实验结果亮点</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Prefill 阶段加速60%</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">吞吐量提升6.4倍</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">KV Cache 压缩至4.74%</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517124\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0738255033557047\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"447\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85b244d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOTOzMW434thfrzmNXhvIeFNlYGfbCSkRnmkApP01ew1FoZtz9ibxlNNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">极端压缩率下依旧保证模型的性能</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503517125\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6905829596412556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"446\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d34c3975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9hBqUz0Dian1TicUfJ9ibOskOtP2teFiaHNBtlZtuE326paHdrqSGehoOOPVZje3nfcibCTgAwib4vv1Ew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过合并检索层和最后的层大海捞针</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">性能几乎无损</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在特定任务上超越全尺寸基线。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们相信，UNCOMP 不仅是一个工具，更是一扇窗口，帮助我们理解 LLM 内部复杂的信息压缩行为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">欢迎大家深入探讨、引用和 star！</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章提出“截断矩阵熵”理论，解释 LLM 稀疏性，并基于此设计 UNCOMP 框架，显著加速 LLM 推理并压缩 KV Cache。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章提出“截断矩阵熵”理论，解释 LLM 稀疏性，并基于此设计 UNCOMP 框架，显著加速 LLM 推理并压缩 KV Cache。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 UNCOMP 论文，该论文被 EMNLP 2025 接收，旨在解决大型语言模型（LLM）中结构化稀疏性缺乏统一理论解释的问题。作者提出了“截断矩阵熵”这一新理论视角，通过分析 Token 矩阵协方差奇异值分布的“拐点”，发现截断矩阵熵随层数加深呈现逐层递减趋势，完美解释了深层网络的稀疏化现象，为模型压缩提供了坚实理论依据。该理论进一步指导了关键结构（如检索层和检索头）的识别，并通过模仿原始信息流模式实现 KV Cache 的最优压缩。基于此，UNCOMP 框架首次实现了通过压缩 Prefill 阶段隐藏状态来间接优化 KV Cache，同时在 Prefill 阶段加速 60%、吞吐量提升 6.4 倍，并将 KV Cache 压缩至 4.74%，且在极端压缩下仍能保证模型性能。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "引入“截断矩阵熵”理论，首次解释 LLM 深层网络稀疏化现象",
      "explanation": "该理论通过关注 Token 矩阵协方差奇异值分布的主成分，揭示信息熵随层数加深而递减，为模型压缩提供了坚实理论基础。"
    },
    {
      "point": "基于信息流模式指导压缩，识别关键结构并优化性能",
      "explanation": "通过分析熵的波动识别检索层和检索头，并模仿原始信息压缩模式进行 KV Cache 压缩，确保性能最优。"
    },
    {
      "point": "UNCOMP 框架实现隐藏状态与 KV Cache 的联合优化",
      "explanation": "通过层级压缩 Prefill 阶段隐藏状态和头级压缩 Decoding 阶段 KV Cache，显著提升推理速度和内存效率。"
    }
  ],
